      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Levels of testing:\n   - System Tests\n        - one or two tests, making an http request and inspecting the response. Done.\n          probably not a single unit test.\n    - Unit Tests\n        - Unit Integration Tests\n            - testing a technical requirement (NFR)\n    - System Integration Tests",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Levels of testing:\n   - System Tests\n        - one or two tests, making an http request and inspecting the response. Done.\n          probably not a single unit test.\n    - Unit Tests\n        - Unit Integration Tests\n            - testing a technical requirement (NFR)\n    - System Integration Tests",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
